HOTELS.longText: Conveniently located near hotspots for shopping and leisure, the NH Las Rozas Aparthotel in Madrid is an oasis of comfort, culture, and convenience. Our proximity to the train station, as well as to the M-40 and N-VI highways, makes the NH Las Rozas hotel an ideal starting point to all destinations in and around the city. Just minutes from our doors, Las Rozas Village and Heron City offer hours of shopping, dining and entertainment. The NH Las Rozas Aparthotel is a newly constructed building offering spacious and stylishly appointed guest quarters. All our Standard Rooms are equipped with plush bedding, elegant wood floors, and a host of thoughtful amenities. Our Superior Rooms are ideal for extended stays, providing an apartment-like layout with a full kitchen and separate living area. Your reservation at the NH Las Rozas Aparthotel includes complimentary wireless internet access and a free continental breakfast every day of your stay. In addition to accommodating both short and long-term guests, the NH Las Rozas Aparthotel also serves as an ideal setting for private events for up to 45 people.

HOTELS.name: NH Las Tablas
HOTELS.shortText: Opened in January 2009, the four-star NH Las Tablas hotel is located in one of Madrid's most prestigious locales. Free Entrance to the Spa for hotel guests!
HOTELS.longText: Opened in January 2009, the four-star NH Las Tablas hotel in Madrid is located in one of Madrid's most prestigious locales. The hotel is nestled between the northern residential areas of Las Tablas and Sanchinarro near La Ciudad de las Comunicaciones and other important business centers. Also convenient to the hotel is a large shopping center, which is only a five-minute walk away. Avante-garde decor and top-quality furnishings and amenities are found in the NH Las Tablas hotel's 149 fully-soundproofed rooms. Each one comes with all the amenities you’d expect from a hotel of this calibre, including bathrooms with full amenities and hairdryer, LCD satellite TV, CD player, WiFi Internet access, a safe and a minibar. All rooms have views out onto the charming Las Tablas town. The hotel’s Superior Rooms and its exclusive Junior Suite offer even more amenities. The NH Las Tablas hotel restaurant offers a delicious breakfast buffet and wide variety of cuisines and dishes for lunch and dinner. For business travelers, the hotel has eight function rooms ranging in size from 27 to 340 meters squared. The latest business technology is on offer in each of the rooms, which suit any type of meeting from presentations to conferences to social celebrations. The hotel's full-service spa is a vast 200 square meters and offers pools, hydromassage, Turkish bath, sauna and gym. Parking is available.Free Entrance to the Spa for hotel guests!(Treatments not included)

HOTELS.name: NH Leganés
HOTELS.shortText: The stylish NH Leganés hotel in Madrid enjoys a prime location in the Nuestra Señora de Butarque Business Park. It is just minutes away from the city's foremost business centers and from the twin campuses of Carlos III University.
HOTELS.longText: The stylish NH Leganés hotel in Madrid enjoys a prime location in the Nuestra Señora de Butarque Business Park. It is just minutes away from the city's foremost business centers and from the twin campuses of Carlos III University. Guests find the Parquesur shopping center right next door and it is just a 20 minute drive to the Xanadú mall with its thrilling indoor ski slope.It is easy to reach downtown Madrid from the NH Leganés hotel. This is a great location to explore the city's older and more unusual stores. However, no trip is complete without a visit to the Plaza Norte 2 and Sexta Avenida, both of which are renowned for fashion outlets. The NH Leganés in Madrid is ideal for families and kids love the excitement of the Warner Brothers theme park which is just 24 kilometers away.The slightly more distant Parque de Attraciones is also well worth a visit, while the Madrid Zoo and Aquarium are a must for animal lovers. There are also two large waterparks within comfortable driving distance of the NH Leganés: the Aquópolis de Villanueva de la Cañada and the Aquópolis de San Fernando de Henares. The NH Leganés hotel itself has plenty to offer for guests who want to stay around their room or take advantage of the facilities and amenities. A bright, spacious lobby with comfortable seating and vending machines is ideal for relaxing or meeting family, friends and clients, and free Wi-Fi offers lots of flexibility for guests to use their laptops around the hotel. There is a stylish breakfast room and the 78 guest rooms are all attractively furnished in a modern style. Guests park for free at the NH Leganés and all the hotel facilities are wheelchair accessible. The NH Leganés hotel in Madrid prides itself on its location, friendly and helpful service, as well as quality rooms.The hotel parking area will be closed for renovation until further notice.

HOTELS.name: NH Monte Rozas
HOTELS.shortText: The NH Monte Rozas hotel offers travelers a strategic location on the road between Las Rozas and El Escorial, just outside Madrid, Spain.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Monte Rozas hotel offers travelers a strategic location on the road between Las Rozas and El Escorial, just outside Madrid, Spain. This friendly and well-equipped hotel in the NH Express line, featuring great rates, fast service, and all the comforts and Internet connectivity you need, is specifically designed to meet the needs of business clients by providing a convenient place to stay near the junction of the A-6 and M-50 motorways. The NH Monte Rozas hotel’s modern styling, comfort, and room amenities ensure a restful and productive stay.Situated just 18 kilometers from downtown Madrid, the NH Monte Rozas hotel offers excellent value and easy access to many locations, including the Madrid city center, new Europolis business district, Las Rozas Business Center, brand new Heron City amusement center, and the Las Rozas Village and Factory Las Rozas shopping centers. In addition, the NH Monte Rozas hotel is near major Spanish cultural and natural sites such as the El Escorial royal monastery and palace as well as the Valle de los Caídos basiclia and memorial.NH Monte Rozas is a three-star hotel offering 63 guestrooms equipped with twin or queen-size beds. Smoking and non-smoking rooms are available. Rooms are equipped with numerous amenities to ensure your comfortable stay, including air conditioning, Satellite TV, direct-dial phones, wireless Internet access, and private bathrooms. Baby cots and a choice of pillows are available on request. Other convenient on-site facilities include currency exchange and a business area with a computer, as well as baggage storage.

HOTELS.name: NH Nacional
HOTELS.shortText: The hotel occupies a historic building dating back to 1920. Recently refurbished and restored to its former glory, in line with the NH Hotels philosophy, it is within walking distance of the "Art Triangle", formed by the Prado Museum, the Thyssen Bornemisza Museum and the Centro de Arte Reina Sofía.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Nacional hotel in Madrid occupies a historic building dating back to 1920. Recently refurbished and restored to its former glory, in line with the NH Hoteles philosophy, it is within walking distance of the "Art Triangle", formed by the Prado Museum, the Thyssen Bornemisza Museum and the Centro de Arte Reina Sofía. It is also conveniently located near the Atocha railway station in the heart of the city and overlooks the Botanical Gardens. Attractive shopping areas, good restaurants and elegant nightclubs are an easy stroll from the NH Nacional in Madrid city center.The NH Nacional hotel in Madrid boasts particularly high quality services and facilities, providing an attractive and relaxing setting alongside the most sophisticated technologies able to meet all the requirements of its tourist and business guests. This attractive setting makes it perfect base for business trips, meetings and cultural visits.All the attractive 214 rooms are comfortably-furnished and equipped with air conditioning, satellite television, radio, direct dial telephone, and minibar. Bathrooms are provided with a bath , hair dryer and complimentary toiletries. The large lobby is a perfect place to meet people. For disabled rooms, please contact the hotel directly. The NH Nacional hotel also offers conference facilities and use of the car park.

HOTELS.name: NH Pacífico
HOTELS.shortText: The NH Pacifico hotel in Madrid first opened its doors in 2005, welcoming world travelers looking for simple elegance and style during their stay in the Spanish capital.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Pacifico hotel in Madrid first opened its doors in 2005, welcoming world travelers looking for simple elegance and style during their stay in the Spanish capital. The NH Pacifico hotel is ideally located for both business and pleasure travel, close to major transportation hubs. The hotel is approximately 15 kilometers from the Madrid-Barajas Airport and close to both the Mendez Alvaro Bus Station and the Atocha Train Station.Lovers of art and culture will especially appreciate how closely situated the NH Pacifico hotel is to several main attractions in Madrid. The city’s famous Art Triangle is located nearby, made up of Madrid’s top three art museums: the Prado Museum, the Reina Sofia Museum of Modern Art and the Thyssen-Bornemisza Museum. Beautiful Retiro Park is steps away from the NH Pacifico. The rest of the city is easily accessible as well. The hotel is surrounded by several bus and subway stops.The NH Pacifico in Madrid is decorated in a comfortable, contemporary style, with a décor that is complemented by warm, earthy colors. The hotel is made up of 62 rooms, with Standard Rooms and Superior Rooms. Guests of the NH Pacifico hotel in Madrid enjoy full amenities such as, wireless internet access, air-conditioning, and satellite television, as well as in-room safety deposit boxes, mini-bars, telephones and private bathrooms. Hotel management at NH Pacifico is committed to high quality service to all guests. The front desk is open 24 hours a day, every day, so guests can rest assured that all their needs are taken care of. The concierge is happy to assist guests with restaurant, museum and ticket reservations. Wireless internet (WiFi) is available throughout the public areas of the hotel.

HOTELS.name: NH Palacio de Tepa
HOTELS.shortText: Located in Madrid's Las Letras district, the NH Palacio de Tepa is surrounded by history and romance. Just a five-minute walk away, the famous Plaza Mayor and next to Plaza Santa Ana enchant tourists and locals alike.
HOTELS.longText: Located in the Las Letras district, the NH Palacio de Tepa hotel in Madrid is surrounded by history and romance. Just a five-minute walk away guests can visit the famous Plaza Mayor and next to Plaza Santa Ana enchant tourists and locals alike. Madrid's most significant museums, such as the Prado Museum, Reina Sofia Art Centre, and Thyssen-Bornemisza Museum, are also nearby, beckoning visitors with priceless works of art.At the NH Palacio de Tepa hotel, our 85 elegantly furnished guest accommodations include unique two-story suites. Each room features singular details reflecting the hotel's 18th century Spanish architecture, with recent renovations that add modern convenience to historical splendor. Ideal for business and leisure travelers alike, our rooms include luxury amenities such as iPod speakers, Wi-Fi, and gym access.Plan a day of sightseeing in Madrid or a productive professional event in one of our fully equipped meeting rooms available at the NH Palacio de Tepa. Then, when it's time to take a break, Chef Paco Roncero will delight your palate with his classic Spanish cuisine at the famous Estado Puro tapas bar.

HOTELS.name: NH Parla
HOTELS.shortText: With its location in the rapidly growing neighborhood of Parla Sur, the NH Parla hotel in Madrid is a perfect choice for travelers to Spain’s capital on business or leisure.
HOTELS.longText: With its location in the rapidly growing neighborhood of Parla Sur, the NH Parla hotel in Madrid is a perfect choice for travelers to Spain’s capital on business or leisure. Just minutes from the NH Parla are the Parque Warner Madrid (Warner Bros theme park) and numerous restaurants, supermarkets, shops and playgrounds. The NH Parla hotel is just off the A-42 motorway, providing quick and easy access to the spectacular cities of Madrid and Toledo, and public transportation is also just steps away.All of the 88 rooms and suites at the NH Parla have been designed for clean, efficient comfort at a price that offers incredible value. Modern amenities such as wireless internet, TV, telephones and adjustable air-conditioning and heat are standard in every room. Families can easily add a rollaway bed or connect adjoining rooms for extra space. We want you feel at home while you are staying at the NH Parla hotel, so even your pet is welcome upon request. A tasty continental breakfast buffet is waiting every morning for guests, and our courtyard café and bar is a great spot for a drink or a meal during your stay in Madrid. All of the facilities at the NH Parla hotel have been recently renovated, creating a fresh modern atmosphere throughout the property.Special events and important business meetings can also be arranged in one of the five multipurpose function rooms at the NH Parla hotel, or outside in our huge private garden area. Up to 350 guests can be accommodated for an event, perfect for a festive wedding celebration or business conference. Our staff at the NH Parla in Madrid is fully trained to help with event planning and execution, and is always ready to make your stay as pleasant as possible.

HOTELS.name: NH Parque Avenidas
HOTELS.shortText: With a prime location in Madrid's chic Salamanca neighborhood near the Las Ventas bullring, the NH Parque Avenidas boasts a swimming pool, a garden, and tennis courts for our guests' enjoyment---plus free WiFi in our hotel lobby.
HOTELS.longText: With a prime location in the chic Salamanca neighborhood near the Las Ventas bullring, the NH Parque Avenidas hotel in Madrid boasts a swimming pool, a garden, and tennis courts for ours guests' enjoyment---plus free WiFi in our hotel lobby. Additionally, our location provides easy access to the M-30 highway, the airport, and the IFEMA fairgrounds.The NH Parque Avenidas hotel spans a large area of 400 square meters as well as a pleasant garden and terrace measuring over 900 square meters. We offer numerous choices for private events such as cocktails, aperitifs, coffee breaks, and more. Chef Joel Tomás, with over 30 years' experience, has created Tendido 7, our innovative restaurant where rice is paired delectably with other Spanish favorites. Our stylish whiskey bar, Park Avenue Bar Terraza, features a large terrace overlooking our garden and pool. Guest will enjoy drinking one of our specialty cocktails while listening to music and relaxing with friends.The NH Parque Avenidas hotel also offers 26 function rooms with capacities ranging from 25 people to more than 800. You select the arrangement, and our team will configure it to perfectly suit your convention, banquet, company meeting, conference, or other type of event. These modern and functional spaces are fitted with every possible technical and personal resource needed for your event to be a success.

HOTELS.name: NH Práctico
HOTELS.shortText: The NH Práctico is a fantastic option for both business and leisure travelers in Madrid looking for a comfortable stay in an intimate, yet modern, environment.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Práctico hotel in Madrid is a fantastic option for both business and leisure travelers in Madrid looking for a comfortable stay in an intimate, yet modern, environment. The NH Práctico is a three-star hotel that offers 40 standard rooms, available with single, double or queen size beds, with smoking and non-smoking options. Modern room amenities include LAN Internet access, satellite television, and air conditioning. Business travelers can take advantage of the hotel’s meeting room, perfect for small business gatherings.The NH Práctico hotel is your gateway to Madrid’s commercial center and beyond, located less than a five-minute walk to the Chamartin train station. In less than 15 minutes, you will be transported to the heart of Madrid, which features landmarks like Plaza del Sol and Plaza Mayor. The NH Práctico is also found near famous Plaza de Castilla, which features two of the highest skyscrapers in Madrid, in addition to seasonal expositions in its park. The hotel is also within easy access to major highways like the N-1, the M-30 and the M-40, enabling you to easily explore the greater Madrid metropolitan area.

HOTELS.name: NH San Sebastián de los Reyes
HOTELS.shortText: The NH San Sebastian de los Reyes hotel offers an excellent location just 20 minutes outside Madrid in the city of San Sebastian de los Reyes.
HOTELS.longText: The NH San Sebastian de los Reyes hotel offers an excellent location just 20 minutes outside Madrid in the city of San Sebastian de los Reyes. The hotel is situated between a major technology and industrial zone and a residential neighborhood, with easy access from the A-1, M-40, and M-50 motorways. The large Plaza Norte II shopping center is just five minutes walking distance from the NH San Sebastian de los Reyes hotel, featuring major stores and factory outlets, as well as the theme-oriented Micropolix entertainment center.The NH San Sebastian de los Reyes hotel offers 99 outward-facing rooms, all tastefully designed with contemporary styling, warm color tones, and all the amenities you need to feel at home during your business and pleasure travel to the Madrid area. Amenities include air conditioning, Satellite TV, Wi-Fi Internet access, an electronic safe, mini-bar, and a fully equipped private bathroom. With standard and deluxe rooms, and a luxurious suite, our accommodations are known for offering comfort and functionality at a great value. For your business and private events, the NH San Sebastian de los Reyes hotel offers two flexible multipurpose rooms that can be combined to hold up to 170 people for receptions. These rooms may be arranged in a variety of different layouts to meet your needs for everything from presentations and conferences to social events and family celebrations. Both meeting rooms benefit from natural daylight, garden access, air-conditioning, and soundproofing. Parking is available directly at the hotel.

HOTELS.name: NH Sanvy
HOTELS.shortText: Experience the best of Spain in the heart of its capital at NH Sanvy. With a prime location in Madrid's Salamanca District, "The Gold Mile", you will find yourself just minutes from the city’s prized shopping, business and cultural areas, including Plaza Colón, Paseo de las Castellana, Prado Museum, Thyssen Bornemisza Museum and Reina Sofia Museum.
HOTELS.longText: Experience the best of Spain at the NH Sanvy hotel in Madrid. With a prime location in the heart of this capital city, in the Salamanca District, "The Gold Mile", you will find yourself just minutes from the city’s prized shopping, business and cultural areas, including the Plaza Colón, Paseo de las Castellana, Prado Museum, Thyssen Bornemitza and Reina Sofia.Our city hotel offers everything you need for a comfortable stay. 146 beautiful guest rooms and suites will be your home away from home at the NH Sanvy hotel. You can soak up the Madrid sun in our terrace solarium, work up a sweat in our gym, and then take a refreshing dip in the nearby swimming pool.Plan your personal or business event in style in our meeting rooms at the NH Sanvy in Madrid – all fully equipped and all offering superior settings. Our exclusive restaurant, 99 Sushi Bar, is a must-try, serving delicious traditional and innovative Japanese cuisine.

HOTELS.name: NH Suites Prisma
HOTELS.shortText: Located in a pedestrian area, the NH Prisma is the ideal location in Madrid for those traveling for business or pleasure. The hotel is located in the neighborhood of Chamberi, and the historic center of Madrid is located just 10 minutes away from the hotel.
HOTELS.longText: Located in a pedestrian area, the NH Prisma hotel in Madrid is the ideal location for those traveling for business or pleasure. The hotel is located in the neighborhood of Chamberi, and the historic center of Madrid is located just 10 minutes away from the hotel. NH Prisma affords easy access to the IFEMA trade fair ground as well as to major transportation links, as well as a subway stop immediately in front of the hotel. The NH Prisma hotel is also within convenient distance from the famous Puerta del Sol, Plaza Mayor and Cibeles. Rooms in the hotel are clean, comfortable and spacious, and are decorated beautifully with warm natural colors. Guests can choose from standard rooms, deluxe rooms and junior suites, all of which offer all of the amenities that you may need.The NH Prisma Suites hotel is made up of three separate buildings with a public parking garage that is perfect for guests traveling with a rental car. For guests who would like a meal without leaving the hotel, there is a beautiful restaurant that offers a beautiful breakfast buffet and a lunch menu. The hotel also has four convention halls that are completely equipped for any type of event.

HOTELS.name: NH Sur
HOTELS.shortText: The NH Sur is a three-star hotel located near the center of Madrid, Spain’s lively capital city. As the hotel is found so close to Madrid’s city center, it is the perfect place for both leisure and business travelers visiting the capital.
HOTELS.longText: The three-star NH Sur hotel in Madrid is located near the center of Madrid, Spain’s lively capital city. As the hotel is found so close to Madrid’s city center, it is the perfect place for both leisure and business travelers visiting the capital. Staying at the NH Sur hotel makes access to the rest of the city a breeze. Madrid’s main train station, Atocha, is located directly across from the hotel. If you’re planning on visiting one of the towns just outside Madrid, be sure to hop on one of the famous high-speed AVE trains.Many of Madrid’s main attractions are within a short walk of the NH Sur hotel. Art lovers will delight in knowing that the world-famous Prado Museum, widely considered to be the best art museum in Spain, is just a five-minute walk away. Nearby is the Reina Sofia Museum, which features a wide collection of contemporary art. Just a few steps away from the Prado Museum lies the Paseo del Prado, one of Madrid’s most beautiful avenues. Enjoy a stroll down the Paseo until you reach the Cibeles fountain, directly across from the stunning Palacio de Telecomunicaciones. The city’s postal headquarters is a cathedral-like landmark, and an absolute must-see when visiting Madrid.Just a short subway ride from the NH Sur hotel is Puerta del Sol, known as the heart of Madrid. Puerta del Sol is famous for its large Clock Tower and the well-known “Tio Pepe” neon lights. Mayor Street extends outwards from Puerta del Sol, and meanders by classic tapas bars, the Plaza Mayor square and the San Miguel market. The San Miguel market is a historic building where you can enjoy some of the best of Madrid’s typical foods. From Puerta del Sol, venture across Preciados Street to Madrid’s main shopping area. After a busy day trying on the hippest Spanish trends, flaunt your style at the nearby theater district and catch a show.The NH Sur in Madrid spans eight floors, with 68 comfortable guest rooms. Each guest room features amenities like flat-screen televisions, telephones and wireless Internet access. Start your day off right by enjoying our delicious breakfast buffet. Tasty highlights include Spanish dishes like “churros” and “tortilla de patatas”. You can host business meetings, conferences and other special events in our meeting room. Stay connected at our lobby and business area, which offers free Wi-Fi, a personal computer and printer for all your needs.

HOTELS.name: NH Victoria Palace
HOTELS.shortText: Just 50 kilometers from Madrid in a setting of exquisite natural beauty, the NH Victoria Palace hotel in San Lorenzo de El Escorial can be found just 200 meters from the El Escorial monastery and palace, which is considered to be one of the architectural marvels of the world.
HOTELS.longText: Just 50 kilometers from Madrid in a setting of exquisite natural beauty, the NH Victoria Palace hotel in San Lorenzo de El Escorial can be found just 200 meters from the El Escorial monastery and palace, which is considered to be one of the architectural marvels of the world. The "Valle de los Caidos" (Valley of the Fallen) is also just eight kilometers away.The new and contemporary décor of NH Victoria Palace's 78 rooms is perfectly integrated into the traditional style of the buiding, providing a clean and simple backdrop to set off the ornate beauty of the palace's original design elements. All rooms are exterior and offer superb views of our peaceful surroundings, as well as an extensive range of amenities to ensure a pleasant, restful stay. Start your day with our wonderful breakfast buffet, while later you can enjoy our Renacimiento restaurant's delicious Spanish regional cuisine for lunch and dinner. Take in the views of the Madrid skyline while you dine---and guests can even choose to eat outdoors on the terrace in temperate weather. For those organizing business events as well as formal or informal gatherings, the NH Victoria Palace hotel's function rooms and events services are well equipped to host any type of work-related function or group celebration.In addition to the terrace, nice days are perfect for enjoying the hotel’s beautifully maintained gardens and outdoor swimming pool. Moreover, NH Victoria Palace hotel in Escorial is located within close proximity of a golf course, and offers convenient access to a range of cultural and recreational activities, such as the Real Teatro of Carlos III, the Auditorium, and the “Gran Madrid” Casino.

HOTELS.name: NH Villa de Coslada
HOTELS.shortText: The NH Villa de Coslada hotel just outside Madrid, Spain, is located in the new residential area of Coslada, between the Industrial Park, new European Transport Center (CET), Barajas Airport, and the Juan Carlos I convention center.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Villa de Coslada hotel just outside Madrid, Spain, is located in the new residential area of Coslada, between the Industrial Park, new European Transport Center (CET), Barajas Airport, and the Juan Carlos I convention center. With easy access to the N-II and M-40 motorways, the NH Villa de Coslada hotel is also well served by public transportation. You can reach the historic center of Madrid by train in just twenty minutes. There are numerous restaurants right by the NH Villa de Coslada hotel, along with many other convenient services, including shops, a supermarket, banks, and a pharmacy.The NH Villa de Coslada hotel offers 78 spacious, well-equipped, and stylish rooms. Relax in the calm comfort of your room after a busy day sightseeing or working. All rooms are equipped with the amenities you need to feel at home, including air conditioning, a desk and chair, Wi-Fi Internet access, a telephone, flat-screen TV, well-stocked mini-bar, and a private bathroom with hairdryer and bathroom amenities. Superior rooms offer even more exclusive features, including access to a superb terrace. The welcoming light-filled restaurant on the first floor of the hotel serves a delicious breakfast buffet with a wide variety of fresh products. The lobby bar provides a relaxing space to sit back and relax for fresh drinks and cocktails.For your business and private events, the NH Villa de Coslada hotel offers six fully-equipped multi-purpose rooms, with capacity to hold up to 500 people. All rooms are soundproofed and benefit from natural daylight, air-conditioning, and all the latest conference equipment. Whether you are organizing a business meeting or a romantic wedding, the NH Villa de Coslada hotel is the ideal place for your event. Parking is available directly at the hotel.

HOTELS.name: NH Zurbano
HOTELS.shortText: NH Zurbano is just a four-minute stroll from the Paseo de la Castellana and close to the Nuevos Ministerios financial district and the Azca business center.
HOTELS.longText: The NH Zurbano hotel in Madrid is just a four-minute stroll from the Paseo de la Castellana and close to the Nuevos Ministerios financial district and the Azca business center. It is also near Madrid's most prestigious shopping area (Serrano Street) and some of its best restaurants.The city center (Puerta del Sol and Gran Via) can be reached in less than 15 minutes by metro and the station is located right in front of the NH Zurbano hotel. There is a direct connection by metro to the airport, with a baggage check-in service provided, as well as to the Juan Carlos 1 Trade Fair Center. The Santiago Bernabeu Stadium is a 10-minute walk away. The NH Zurbano offers 266 rooms, including 40 Superior rooms, 10 Junior Suites and 1 Suite, room service, a breakfast buffet and an a la carte restaurant. There is also a fitness center located close to the hotel, where guests can keep fit during their stay at a special discounted rate.
